---
title: Grilled Tenderloin Steak and Stone Fruit Panzanella with Bocconcini and Balsamic Glaze
description: Tenderloin steak is the supreme topper for this loaded panzanella bowl. Featuring grilled stone fruit, crunchy cucumbers, heirloom baby tomatoes and marinated bocconcini, this meal is sure to be a summer hit!
